BT /F1 9 Tf 42 697 Td (easy to start with, but they become brittle as prompt variety grows. A classifier lets the) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 42 686 Td (system learn patterns from labeled examples, improves consistency, and creates a path for) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 42 675 Td (retraining as new prompt types appear.) Tj ET
